onents of $f^{-1}(s)$ for $s\\in T_f$ are also described - they have a\nfinite graph structure. We give an example of a uniform quotient map from\n$R^2\\to R$ which has non-locally connected level sets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 Jan 2003 11:01:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
